title: Hour 2 - Draymond Won't Change, Daniel Snyder Details

description:
Dan considers the repercussions for Golden State Warriors F Draymond Green and whether his behavior and attitude will ever change. And he digs into exactly what's going on with Washington Commanders Owner, Daniel Snyder.
